displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Ludhiana, India.

highlights.text: Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Ludhiana. Never Fold is the highest at #14.
FRIEND ZONE by Jass Bajwa and Mandeep Maavi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ludhiana at #18.
Kahani Suno 2.0 by Kaifi Khalil is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ludhiana, up 32 spots at #42.
Baller by Shubh and Ikky has been on Top Songs Ludhiana the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
